main_body:
In Article 1 of Regulation (EC) No 1103/97:
(a) the words "or in accordance with paragraph 5 of that Article" shall be added at the end of the third indent;
(b) the words "or, as the case may be, on the day before the euro is substituted for the currency of a Member State which adopts the euro at a later date" shall be added at the end of the fourth indent.
